{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c97c9e1a-ccc0-4227-8a5b-a11fdc0ee252","content":"In .NET MAUI, those `Application`-level overrides are replaced by **`Window` lifecycle events**. Override `CreateWindow` in your `App` class and subscribe to events on the `Window`:\n\n```csharp\nprotected override Window CreateWindow(IActivationState? activationState)\n{\n    var window = base.CreateWindow(activationState);\n\n    window.Created += (s, e) => { /* replaces OnStart */ };\n    window.Stopped += (s, e) => { /* replaces OnSleep */ };\n    window.Resumed += (s, e) => { /* replaces OnResume */ };\n\n    return window;\n}\n```\n\nAlternatively, subclass `Window` and override `OnCreated()`, `OnStopped()`, and `OnResumed()` directly.\n\nOther useful `Window` events: `Activated`, `Deactivated`, `Destroying`, `Backgrounding` (iOS/Mac).","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0461aa57-2efd-4932-a3c4-183ddc4bb93d","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating lifecycle methods from Xamarin.Forms to .NET MAUI. This is a knowledge question I can answer directly without needing to search the codebase.\n\nIn Xamarin.Forms, you'd override `OnStart()`, `OnSleep()`, and `OnResume()` on the `Application` class.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, the lifecycle model changed. Instead of those virtual methods on `Application`, you use the `Window` lifecycle events or the cross-platform lifecycle events via `ConfigureLifecycleEvents` in `MauiProgram.cs`, or you can override lifecycle methods on the `Window` class.\n\n\nThe mapping is more granular in MAUI—`OnStart` maps to `Window.Created`, `OnSleep` to `Window.Deactivated` or `Window.Stopped`, and `OnResume` to `Window.Resumed` or `Window.Activated`. You can either override the lifecycle methods directly on a custom `Window` subclass like `OnCreated()`, `OnActivated()`, `OnDeactivated()`, `OnStopped()`, `OnResumed()`, and `OnDestroying()`, or subscribe to the corresponding Window events instead.","outputTokens":626,"requestId":"DBCB:931B0:9F1FE:C97C9:69F54B10"},"id":"5982f4f9-1428-49f6-a609-73bbd4335bfd","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:53:48.916Z","parentId":"35e56715-ab5d-45ef-8620-e953f21c6524"}
